<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Your Dining Room Is Full.<br /><span class="text-gradient">Your Phone Is Ignored.</span></h2>
      <p>
        During peak hours, your staff is seating guests and managing the floor—not answering calls.
        Customers call, hang up, and book elsewhere. You never see the loss.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">$3,000-$5,000</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Lost Per Month</div>
        <p class="stat-description">
          Missed reservations quietly drain revenue. Each unanswered call during peak hours
          could mean a table of 4 booking at your competitor instead.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">70%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Don't Call Back</div>
        <p class="stat-description">
          When customers can't reach you, they don't try again. They search for
          "restaurants near me" and book the next available option.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">Peak Hours</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Highest Intent</div>
        <p class="stat-description">
          Callers during your busiest times are the most ready to dine. They've made their
          decision—they just need someone to answer the phone.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-visual">
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-icon missed">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72"/>
              <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <strong>7:15 PM - Call Missed</strong>
            <p>Party of 6 looking to book for tonight</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-icon missed">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72"/>
              <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <strong>7:23 PM - Call Missed</strong>
            <p>Customer asking about gluten-free options</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-icon missed">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72"/>
              <line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <strong>7:31 PM - Call Missed</strong>
            <p>Couple wanting to modify their 8 PM reservation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-caption">
        <strong>This happens every night.</strong> Your staff is doing their job—serving guests.
        But every missed call is missed revenue.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .stat-card {
    position: relative;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    cursor: default;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: bottom;
    transition: transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .stat-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleY(1);
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(10px);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .stat-card:hover .stat-number {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .stat-description {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .problem-visual {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.75rem;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-icon {
    position: absolute;
    left: calc(-1 * var(--space-xl) - 0.25rem);
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-icon.missed {
    border-color: var(--color-error);
    color: var(--color-error);
    background: #fef2f2;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .timeline-content strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline-caption {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: #fef2f2;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-error);
  }

  .timeline-caption strong {
    color: var(--color-error);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
